title: 139: The Target Snacks & Sips Haul Episode
itunes:title: The Target Snacks & Sips Haul Episode
description: In this episode, Lisa, Jamie, and Mikey are trying some really great food finds like a vanilla cinnamon coconut smoothie, a super-cute charcuterie snack, a cranberry pumpkin artisanal crisp that tastes like pretzels, chocolate-covered almonds, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, the top find of the week, frozen fruit & yogurt bites that will remind you of Dippin’ Dots! No need to wait any longer… Push play now, abd then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of products mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: We hit the bullseye this week with some amazing snack & drink finds at Target!
